1. Open the project using any IDE
2. Rebuild the project by clicking on Build and then Rebuild Project
3. Run mvn compile exec:java command in the terminal or go to Edit Configurations
   and click Add New Configuration and select Maven, then go to Parameters to the
   right and in the command line text box type in exec:java, click apply, and then
   run the the program
4. Once the program is up and running open two different browsers to localhost:4567
5. You can now sign in and play checkers with another player that is also signed in
   or against an AI